0cc92af/Manchester_Piccadilly.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-20T10:02:20.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Investigation into the derailment of a tram at Piccadilly tram stop, Manchester,  5 April 2026.</p>\n</div>","title":"Tram derailment at Piccadilly tram stop"},{"document_type":"Independent report","href":"/government/publications/safety-digest-042026-millbrook","image":{"alt_text":"The access point at Millbrook.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e0a66553469bbcdf408f63/s712_Millbrook.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e0a6656c6ccf244be42e1e/s465_Millbrook.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e0a665f5069cdc548688c2/Millbrook.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-16T10:05:01.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>RAIB has today released its safety digest into a near miss between a passenger train and a van near Millbrook, Bedfordshire, 25 September 2025.</p>\n</div>","title":"Safety digest 04/2026: Millbrook"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/road-vehicle-incursion-at-york-street-belfast","image":{"alt_text":"The HGV vehicle incursion (courtesy of Northern Ireland Railways).","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69df8c8f6c6ccf244be42d7b/s712_York_Street.jpeg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69df8c8f53469bbcdf408ec9/s465_York_Street.jpeg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69df8c8ff5069cdc54868838/York_Street.jpeg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-15T14:02:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Investigation into a near miss between a train and a heavy goods vehicle near York Street, Belfast, 20 March 2026.</p>\n</div>","title":"Road vehicle incursion at York Street, Belfast"},{"document_type":"Independent report","href":"/government/publications/safety-digest-032026-hopetown-junction","image":{"alt_text":"The t